类 QueryUtil

      • getRowKeyUIDRegex

        public static String getRowKeyUIDRegex(List<byte[]> group_bys,
                                       org.hbase.async.Bytes.ByteMap<byte[][]> row_key_literals)
        Crafts a regular expression for scanning over data table rows and filtering time series that the user doesn't want. At least one of the parameters must be set and have values. NOTE: This method will sort the group bys.
        参数:
        group_bys - An optional list of tag keys that we want to group on. May be null.
        row_key_literals - An optional list of key value pairs to filter on. May be null.
        返回:
        A regular expression string to pass to the storage layer.

      • getRowKeyUIDRegex

        public static String getRowKeyUIDRegex(List<byte[]> group_bys,
                                       org.hbase.async.Bytes.ByteMap<byte[][]> row_key_literals,
                                       boolean explicit_tags,
                                       byte[] fuzzy_key,
                                       byte[] fuzzy_mask)
        Crafts a regular expression for scanning over data table rows and filtering time series that the user doesn't want. Also fills in an optional fuzzy mask and key as it builds the regex if configured to do so.
        参数:
        group_bys - An optional list of tag keys that we want to group on. May be null.
        row_key_literals - An optional list of key value pairs to filter on. May be null.
        explicit_tags - Whether or not explicit tags are enabled so that the regex only picks out series with the specified tags
        fuzzy_key - An optional fuzzy filter row key
        fuzzy_mask - An optional fuzzy filter mask
        返回:
        A regular expression string to pass to the storage layer.
        从以下版本开始:
        2.3

      • setDataTableScanFilter

        public static void setDataTableScanFilter(org.hbase.async.Scanner scanner,
                                          List<byte[]> group_bys,
                                          org.hbase.async.Bytes.ByteMap<byte[][]> row_key_literals,
                                          boolean explicit_tags,
                                          boolean enable_fuzzy_filter,
                                          int end_time)
        Sets a filter or filter list on the scanner based on whether or not the query had tags it needed to match. NOTE: This method will sort the group bys.
        参数:
        scanner - The scanner to modify.
        group_bys - An optional list of tag keys that we want to group on. May be null.
        row_key_literals - An optional list of key value pairs to filter on. May be null.
        explicit_tags - Whether or not explicit tags are enabled so that the regex only picks out series with the specified tags
        enable_fuzzy_filter - Whether or not a fuzzy filter should be used in combination with the explicit tags param. If explicit tags is disabled then this param is ignored.
        end_time - The end of the query time so the fuzzy filter knows when to stop scanning.

      • getRowKeyTSUIDRegex

        public static String getRowKeyTSUIDRegex(List<String> tsuids)
        Creates a regular expression with a list of or'd TUIDs to compare against the rows in storage.
        参数:
        tsuids - The list of TSUIDs to scan for
        返回:
        A regular expression string to pass to the storage layer.

      • getMetricScanner

        public static org.hbase.async.Scanner getMetricScanner(TSDB tsdb,
                                                       int salt_bucket,
                                                       byte[] metric,
                                                       int start,
                                                       int stop,
                                                       byte[] table,
                                                       byte[] family)
        Compiles an HBase scanner against the main data table
        参数:
        tsdb - The TSDB with a configured HBaseClient
        salt_bucket - An optional salt bucket ID for salting the start/stop keys.
        metric - The metric to scan for
        start - The start time stamp in seconds
        stop - The stop timestamp in seconds
        table - The table name to scan over
        family - The table family to scan over
        返回:
        A scanner ready for processing.
